ustering coefficient in either of the\nlayers, and we present a map with these values for all regions. The results of\nthis research can help policy making organizations understand the spatial\ndimension of subsidized research and patented innovation collaboration\nnetworks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Nov 2020 16:52:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-10"}
