ficiently general\" discriminantal arrangements. As a\nconsequence, we give a geometric description of the lattice elements as sets of\nconcurrencies of the hyperplane arrangements which give the same \"very generic\nor sufficiently general\" discriminantal arrangement.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 Nov 2020 04:19:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 8 Jun 2021 07:59:34 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 14 Jul 2021 12:43:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-15"}
